    "privacy-section-1-title": "1. Who We Are",
    "privacy-section-1-content": "Gavion\n5835 rue de Cadillac, Montréal, Québec, Canada, H1M 2L6\nEmail: info@gavion.ai\nPhone: +1 (438) 900-4566\n\nIf you have questions about this Privacy Policy or about how we handle personal information, you can contact us using the details above.",
    "privacy-section-2-title": "2. What Personal Information We Collect",
    "privacy-section-2-content": "We may collect personal information that you provide directly to us, including: your name; business name; email address; phone number; job title; city or region; information you include in a contact form, chat, intake form, or demo request; information you provide during calls, consultations, onboarding, or support requests; billing or payment-related contact information, where applicable.\n\nWe may also collect certain technical and usage information automatically when you use our website, such as: IP address; browser type; device type; pages visited; date and time of visits; referral source; approximate location derived from IP; cookie or analytics identifiers.\n\nIf you upload or send documents, FAQs, business information, scripts, call flows, knowledge base content, or other materials to us, those materials may contain personal information depending on what you provide.",
    "privacy-section-3-title": "3. How We Collect Personal Information",
    "privacy-section-3-content": "We collect personal information in several ways, including when you: visit our website; fill out a form; book a call or request a demo; contact us by email, phone, or website chat; subscribe to updates or marketing communications; become a client; provide information during onboarding or support.\n\nWe may also collect information through cookies, analytics tools, pixels, chat widgets, calendars, forms, and similar technologies used on our website.",
