    "privacy-section-16-title": "16. Third-Party Websites",
    "privacy-section-16-content": "Our website may contain links to third-party websites, platforms, or tools. We are not responsible for the privacy practices, content, or security of those third parties. You should review their privacy policies before providing them with personal information.",
    "privacy-section-17-title": "17. Changes to This Privacy Policy",
